                      "description":  "\u003cp\u003eAmerica teaches its own history better than most countries. The problem is what gets left out.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis book covers the episodes that don\u0027t fit neatly into the national mythology. The government programs that deliberately harmed citizens. The corporate interests that shaped foreign policy and started wars. The surveillance programs that predated the internet. The assassinations and suspicious deaths that were ruled out in days and never revisited. The treaties that were made and broken, the populations that were deceived, the promises that were never meant to be kept.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThese are not conspiracy theories. They are documented history, sourced from congressional records, declassified documents, and investigative journalism. The difference between a conspiracy theory and history is often just time and access.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you love America, you can handle knowing the full story. This book is for people who think that\u0027s true.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch6 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTABLE OF CONTENTS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h6\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eINTRODUCTION\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eA brief overview uncovering suppressed truths in US history.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGovernment overreaches that expanded federal power at liberty\u0027s expense.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHidden manipulations by elites shaping America against traditional values.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 1: THE FOUNDING MYTHS ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ LIES BEHIND THE REVOLUTION\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eElite manipulations and foreign influences driving the rebellion for power consolidation.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBetrayals of Loyalists through property seizures and civil war atrocities.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSetting precedents for centralized government overreaches ignoring states\u0027 rights.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 2: SLAVERY\u0027S HIDDEN ARCHITECTS ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ BEYOND THE OBVIOUS NARRATIVES\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNorthern industrialists and bankers profiting from slave labor without direct ownership.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eInternational financiers funding the transatlantic trade for global economic gains.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePolitical elites prolonging bondage through compromises favoring their interests.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 3: THE INDIAN WARS ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ ERASED GENOCIDES AND BROKEN TREATIES\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGovernment deceit and corporate land grabs displacing Native populations.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBrutal military campaigns ignoring treaties for westward expansion.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuppressed Native resistance and cultural erasure challenging frontier myths.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 4: THE MEXICAN-AMERICAN WAR ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ IMPERIAL LAND GRABS AND FORGOTTEN ATROCITIES\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProvoked border incidents as pretexts for territorial seizures expanding slavery.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eUS troops\u0027 massacres of Mexican civilians hidden from public view.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eManifest destiny propaganda deepening North-South divides toward Civil War.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 5: CIVIL WAR SECRETS ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ THE REAL MOTIVATIONS AND COVER-UPS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEconomic tariffs favoring North provoking Southern secession.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNorthern aggression and federal power grabs during the conflict.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePost-war reconstructions entrenching centralized control over states.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 6: THE ROBBER BARONS ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ INDUSTRIAL TYRANNY AND FORGOTTEN VICTIMS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMonopolists crushing competition through predatory practices.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWorker exploitation in factories with deadly conditions ignored.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGovernment favors enabling crony capitalism over free markets.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 7: IMPERIAL AMBITIONS ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ THE SPANISH-AMERICAN WAR DECEPTIONS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFabricated pretexts like the Maine explosion justifying invasion.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMedia manipulations whipping up war fever for colonial gains.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShift to global empire-building under false humanitarian flags.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 8: WORLD WAR I ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ THE BANKERS\u0027 WAR AND SUPPRESSED DISSENT\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFinancial elites dragging US into conflict for loan profits.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGovernment suppression of anti-war voices through laws.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWartime profiteering prolonging the war at public expense.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 9: THE ROARING TWENTIES ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ CORRUPTION BENEATH THE GLAMOUR\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBootlegging empires thriving under Prohibition\u0027s failures.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePolitical scandals like Teapot Dome exposing graft.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEconomic bubbles built on speculation leading to crash.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 10: THE NEW DEAL ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ SOCIALIST EXPERIMENTS AND POWER GRABS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrograms prolonging Depression through price controls.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourt-packing attempts threatening judicial independence.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExpansion of federal bureaucracy eroding states\u0027 rights.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 11: TUSKEGEE EXPERIMENTS ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ MEDICAL DEHUMANIZATION AND RACIAL EXPLOITATION\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGovernment withholding treatment from black subjects for data.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEugenics undertones in unethical medical studies.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eErosion of trust in institutions among minorities.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 12: WORLD WAR II ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ ALLIANCES WITH EVIL AND DOMESTIC BETRAYALS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCompromises with Stalin betraying Eastern Europe.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDomestic internment camps violating civil rights.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWar profiteering and suppressed military atrocities.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 13: THE COLD WAR ORIGINS ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ COMMUNIST INFILTRATION IGNORED\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSoviet spies in government influencing policy.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMedia downplaying red threats for narratives.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMcCarthy\u0027s warnings vindicated by later evidence.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 14: MKULTRA ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ CIA MIND CONTROL AND CITIZEN GUINEA PIGS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIllegal experiments on unwitting Americans using drugs.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eViolations of ethical codes post-WWII.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTesting population control undermining bodily autonomy.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 15: KENNEDY\u0027S ASSASSINATION ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ THE DEEP STATE AWAKENING\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eInconsistencies in official lone gunman narrative.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCIA and mob connections as potential motives.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuppressed evidence pointing to broader conspiracy.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 16: VIETNAM ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ DRAFT DODGES, MEDIA LIES, AND ANTI-WAR HYPOCRISY\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eElite evasions of service while poor fought.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFabricated incidents like Gulf of Tonkin.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProtesters\u0027 communist sympathies dividing movements.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 17: WATERGATE AND BEYOND ΟΔβ²§βÄ€ POLITICAL WITCH HUNTS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMedia amplification of Nixon\u0027s scandal.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIgnored precedents in prior administrations.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cp role=\"presentation\" dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSetting templates for partisan impeachments.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 18: THE REAGAN