                      "description":  "\u003cp\u003eGreek mythology is often presented through its heroes, quests, and epic battles. This book looks at the other side: the cruelty, punishment, betrayal, and moral ambiguity that run through the original myths. From gods who punish humans for minor offenses to stories of murder, transformation, and revenge, Greek mythology has always contained a dark current that modern retellings tend to soften.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis book stays close to the ancient sources and presents the myths as they were originally told, including their most disturbing elements. It examines the cultural logic behind these dark themes and what they reveal about how ancient Greeks understood fate, justice, divine power, and human suffering. The result is a more honest and complete picture of one of history\u0027s most influential mythological traditions.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eReader review:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cem\u003e\"Much better than the sanitized versions. The original myths are genuinely dark and this book doesn\u0027t flinch from that -- very well done.\"\u003c/em\u003e -- S. Papadopoulos\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis title belongs in mythology and classical studies sections. It serves readers who want a more authentic engagement with Greek myth and is a good fit for bookstores, libraries, and wholesale buyers supplying history and mythology sections.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOrder now.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch6 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTABLE OF CONTENTS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h6\u003e\n\u003chr\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1. THE FORBIDDEN ROOTS: HOW INCEST SHAPED THE DIVINE FAMILY TREE\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExplores primordial unions like Gaia and Uranus leading to violent rebellions.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDetails Cronus and Rhea\u0027s sibling marriage and his cannibalism of offspring.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTraces Zeus\u0027s inheritance of incestuous patterns and their ripple into mortal myths.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2. ZEUS UNMASKED: THE THUNDER GOD\u0027S REIGN OF SEXUAL TERROR\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExamines Zeus\u0027s shape-shifting assaults on figures like Europa and Leda.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHighlights incestuous violations within his family, including with relatives like Demeter.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDiscusses patterns of punishment on victims and their offspring, reflecting patriarchal impunity.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3. HERA\u0027S FURY: JEALOUSY AS A WEAPON IN A BROKEN MARRIAGE\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eUnpacks Hera\u0027s vengeful torments on Zeus\u0027s lovers, such as Leto and Io.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnalyzes her campaigns against illegitimate children like Heracles and Dionysus.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProbes the psychological and cultural mirrors of her rage in ancient Greek society.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4. THE UNDERWORLD\u0027S HORRORS: HADES AND THE ETERNAL PRISON OF SOULS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMaps the geography of despair with rivers like Styx and pits like Tartarus.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDetails ironic punishments for the damned, such as Sisyphus and Tantalus.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExplores Hades\u0027s rule and myths of descent challenging the realm\u0027s terrors.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e5. MEDUSA\u0027S CURSE: FROM VICTIM TO MONSTER IN THE EYES OF GODS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTraces Medusa\u0027s origins as a beautiful priestess raped by Poseidon in Athena\u0027s temple.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExamines her transformation and Perseus\u0027s hunt as a divine cover-up.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDiscusses cultural evolutions turning her from monster to feminist icon.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e6. CANNIBAL KINGS: ATREUS AND THE CYCLE OF FAMILIAL DEVOURMENT\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDetails Tantalus\u0027s feast of his son Pelops served to the gods.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eUnpacks Atreus\u0027s revenge banquet of Thyestes\u0027s children.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExplores the chain of vengeance leading to Agamemnon\u0027s and Orestes\u0027s fates.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e7. POSEIDON\u0027S WRATH: OCEANS OF VIOLENCE AND BESTIAL DESIRES\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExamines Poseidon\u0027s assaults in animal forms, like the stallion with Demeter.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHighlights floods and quakes as retribution, such as submerging cities.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDiscusses monstrous offspring from curses, including the Minotaur.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e8. DIONYSUS\u0027S MADNESS: ECSTASY, MURDER, AND HIDDEN CULT SECRETS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDetails Dionysus\u0027s dismemberment as infant Zagreus by Titans.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eUnpacks myths of kings like Pentheus torn apart by maenads.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExplores secretive rites involving frenzy and possible human sacrifices.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e9. ATHENA\u0027S SHADOWS: WISDOM TAINTED BY WAR AND BETRAYAL\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnalyzes Athena\u0027s birth from Zeus\u0027s head after swallowing Metis.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExamines her manipulations, like punishing Arachne and aiding betrayals.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProbes her role in wars and atrocities, including Trojan conflicts.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10. THE TITANOMACHY: COSMIC SLAUGHTER AND THE BIRTH OF TYRANNY\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDetails pre-war tensions with Cronus\u0027s rule and Zeus\u0027s uprising.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eUnpacks key battles involving Cyclopes and Hecatoncheires\u0027 alliances.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExplores the imprisonment of Titans and the emergence of Olympian despotism.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e11. PROMETHEUS BOUND: ETERNAL AGONY AND THE PRICE OF DEFIANCE\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTraces Prometheus\u0027s creation of humans and theft of fire from gods.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExamines his alliance with Zeus in the Titan war and subsequent betrayal.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDetails his chaining and daily liver-eating torment by an eagle.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e12. THE MINOTAUR\u0027S LABYRINTH: BESTIALITY, IMPRISONMENT, AND ROYAL SHAME\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eUnpacks PasiphaΟÉ¬Ϊ\u0027s curse-driven lust for the bull and Minotaur\u0027s birth.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExplores the maze\u0027s construction and imprisonment of the beast.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDiscusses Athens\u0027 youth tributes and Theseus\u0027s quest to slay it.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e13. ORPHEUS\u0027S DESCENT: LOVE, LOSS, AND THE CRUELTY OF THE AFTERLIFE\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDetails Eurydice\u0027s death from a viper bite on their wedding day.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExamines Orpheus\u0027s journey to Hades and the fateful backward glance.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProbes his post-descent isolation, madness, and dismemberment by maenads.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e14. AMAZONIAN BLOODSHED: WARRIOR WOMEN ERASED BY MALE DOMINANCE\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTraces Amazon origins as all-female tribes from Scythian steppes.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eUnpacks battles like Heracles\u0027s girdle quest and Penthesilea\u0027s Trojan stand.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExplores archaeological evidence of real female warriors and their mythic erasure.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e15. SIRENS\u0027 SONG: SEDUCTION LEADING TO MASS DROWNINGS AND DESPAIR\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDetails Sirens\u0027 bird-woman forms and knowledge-promising songs.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExamines Odysseus\u0027s wax-and-rope resistance during his voyage.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProbes Argonauts\u0027 counter with Orpheus\u0027s overpowering music.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e16. THE FATES\u0027 WEB: PREDESTINED DOOM AND THE ILLUSION OF FREE WILL\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eUnpacks the Moirai\u0027s roles in spinning, measuring, and cutting life threads.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExplores how they doomed heroes like Oedipus and Achilles.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDiscusses philosophical debates on fate versus agency in ancient thought.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e17. CRONUS\u0027S SAVAGERY: CHILD-EATING AND THE FEAR OF SUCCESSION\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDetails Cronus\u0027s castration of Uranus and rise to power.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExamines his swallowing of five children to avert prophecy.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProbes historical parallels to tyrants purging their heirs.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e18. EROS AND PSYCHE: FORBIDDEN LOVE MASKING PSYCHOLOGICAL TORTURE\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTraces Psyche\u0027s beauty curse and isolation in Eros\u0027s dark palace.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eUnpacks Aphrodite\u0027s grueling trials designed to break her.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExplores the marriage as reward after torment and its abusive undertones.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e19. TROJAN ATROCITIES: HEROES AS WAR CRIMINALS IN HOMER\u0027S SHADOW\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDetails rapes and enslavements of Trojan women like Briseis and Cassandra.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExamines Achilles\u0027s desecration of Hector\u0027s corpse.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProbes infant slaughters like Astyanax and divine complicity in horrors.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e20. ECHOES IN THE ABYSS: MODERN REVIVALS OF DARK MYTHS AND THEIR DANGERS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExplores Hollywood\u0027s glossing of rapes and tyranny in films like Kaos.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eUnpacks political appropriations by far-right groups for hate rhetoric.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDiscusses psychological perils in games and apps reviving trauma.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eΟ²¬†\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch6\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProduct Details\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h6\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDimensions: \u003cstrong\u003e6 ΟÉβÄî 9 inches / 15.24 x 22.86 cm\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003eCover: \u003cstrong\u003ePaperback\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e",
