                      "description":  "\u003cp\u003eEveryone knows D-Day, Stalingrad, and the Battle of Britain. Fewer people know about the battles that shaped the outcome of the war just as decisively, without ever getting famous.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis book covers the overlooked clashes. The Battle of the Atlantic that came within weeks of starving Britain into surrender. The campaigns in North Africa and their effect on the strategic calculation in Europe. The fighting in Burma and what it cost British and Indian troops. The forgotten battles on the Eastern Front beyond Stalingrad. The Pacific island-hopping campaigns where the casualty rates were staggering and the strategic logic was not always clear at the time. The siege of Malta. The partisan wars in Yugoslavia and their brutal consequences.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWorld War II was fought on more fronts and in more places than the popular narrative suggests. The battles in this book were all significant. Most people have never heard of them.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you know the famous battles, it\u0027s time to know these ones.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch6 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTABLE OF CONTENTS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h6\u003e\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 1: INTRODUCTION\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSets the stage for World War II\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExplains why smaller, lesser-known battles matter\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHighlights the global scope of the conflict\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 2: THE FIRST SPARKS OF CONFLICT\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTraces early tensions and minor border clashes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShows how local incidents hinted at a bigger war\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eReveals the atmosphere in different nations before 1939\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 3: THE BATTLE OF LAKE KHASAN\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDescribes a brief Soviet-Japanese clash in 1938\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEmphasizes how even small fights shaped bigger strategies\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eReveals harsh conditions and rapid troop movements\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 4: THE BATTLE OF KHALKHIN GOL\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExplores a longer Soviet-Japanese conflict in 1939\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDetails evolving tactics and lessons learned by both sides\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHighlights the importance of coordination in remote battlefields\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCHAPTER 5: THE SIEGE OF BREST FORTRESS\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFocuses on early German invasion of the Soviet Union\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExplains how a small garrison held out heroically\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"