vements\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHighlights small groups questioning Swedish dominion and exploring autonomy ideas\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShows war-weary officers and nobles seeking alternatives in secret\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTies cultural pride to emerging notions of FinlandΟΔβ²§β³Δs distinct interests\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eChapter 18: Literary and Educational Changes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCovers the spread of literacy via parish schools and traveling teachers\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDescribes modest expansions in Finnish-language publishing and folklore collecting\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIlluminates the synergy between cultural pride and early political thinking\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eChapter 19: Decline of Swedish Rule and Shifting Powers\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnalyzes the monarchyΟΔβ²§β³Δs financial crises, diplomatic blunders, and repeated defeats\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eExplores how local elites and commoners lost faith in StockholmΟΔβ²§β³Δs ability to protect them\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eReveals how Napoleonic-era upheavals paved the way for FinlandΟΔβ²§β³Δs realignment\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch2 dir=\"lt